org.fhnw.aigs.server.common

Class CustomFormatter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.logging.Formatter
      • org.fhnw.aigs.server.common.CustomFormatter

  • public class CustomFormatter
extends java.util.logging.Formatter
    Custom formatter for logging. This class can switch the logging style ad hoc at runtime. Implemented is XML format, simple format and a compressed format.
    Most parts of XML and simple format are copied from the original Java SE sources.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Raphael Stoeckli (26.02.2015)
